Josh King, welcome to the
"NewsHour."

35:20.685 --> 35:22.354 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSH KING, Author, "Off Script:
Thanks, Judy.
Thanks for having me.

35:22.387 --> 35:24.322 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, first of all,
what is an
advance man?

35:24.356 --> 35:28.493 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSH KING: An advance man is
basically a political
movie producer.

35:28.526 --> 35:32.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We roam the hustings of America
and around
the world trying to tell
political stories

35:32.797 --> 35:38.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
by setting up tableaus that
connect a president
or a presidential candidate with
the places

35:38.236 --> 35:40.238 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
they are or the people that
they're interacting
with.

35:40.271 --> 35:45.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You were there
for some of
the most memorable moments of
the last several

35:45.510 --> 35:50.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
